==Passive Voice?==
This is hardly covered apart from a comment on French's limited passive voice [[French/Grammar/Pronouns#The_pronoun_on|here]], as far as I can make out. The use of "se faire + infinitive" is another passive construction which could be added somewhere. I am not saying these are priorities, but perhaps it is worth checking their prominence in other books. [[User:Recent Runes|Recent Runes]] ([[User talk:Recent Runes|talk]]) 18:48, 18 November 2010 (UTC)

